scarlet mistletoe
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an endangered red-flowered native plant, known variously as  <i>Elytranthe colensoi </i> or <i> Peraxilla colensoi </i>.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:Environment
Region:[none]
